                &lt;span class=&quot;comment-copy&quot;&gt;This is what I do.  With this, you can print arbitrarily complex structures as long as they&apos;re encodable to JSON. I always make sure to use &quot;pretty&quot;.  Does your second example do that?  I&apos;d think you&apos;d need to tickle a &quot;pretty&quot; option to get that.&lt;/span&gt;

